metadata.name: DREAMFYRE-LEAN
metadata.description: Hello! My name is Serotonin and I am a 25-year-old painter. I have always had a love for art and creating, and discovered my passion for painting at a young age. I have been practicing and honing my skills and I enjoy experimenting with different styles and mediums, and am constantly seeking new inspiration for my paintings. My ultimate goal as an artist is to inspire others through my work and to bring beauty and emotion into the world. Thank you for taking the time to learn more about me and my art.
